						<summary>

						

						<p>This is a short inscription in Telugu dated in the cyclic year Viḷambi, Āśvija, śu. 5, Thursday. It mentions <hi rend="bold">Rāmābhaṭṭa Ayyavāru</hi> and one Maddala Basavayya. The former is evidently the same as the minister of <hi rend="bold">Achyuta</hi> who figures in No. 607, dated in Śaka 1456. The cyclic year Viḷambi would then correspond to Śaka 1460 (A.D. 1538-39).</p>						

						</summary>
